{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether this was us, or-- I tend to think that in those days you-- children just did as they were told.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't have the free and open discussions that our children now have with us, where they are able to discuss everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm trying to remember that we ever discussed anything with our parents, and certainly not important things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would discuss with us how we got on at school kind of thing, and what we were doing-- playing and, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think they made us aware of all of the nasty things that were going on around us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not much in Berlin, but I do later on-- later in life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't really know what exactly we played.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that there was a tram, the S-Baun that ran very close to our home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we obviously traveled on that quite often.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, no, I mean I can't remember any games that I played at that time, really.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little, I'm afraid, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just don't remember much about that at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only that I liked school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I always enjoyed school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was always a very keen student.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I always did well at school in most subjects, except music.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was never any good at music and singing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise, in everything, I was keen and to the front and always liked to be top and all those sorts things, yes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Math and maybe even German language and many of the subjects, I think-- most of the things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to enjoy going to school and did well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that's sort of been throughout the various schools that I attended over the next 10 years.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
